Package: freecryptonews
Title: Free Crypto News API Client
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Free Crypto News", email = "developers@cryptocurrency.cv", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R client for the Free Crypto News API (https://cryptocurrency.cv).
    No API key required. Fetch real-time crypto news, search by keyword, filter
    by category (DeFi, Bitcoin), and access 200+ sources.
    Inspired by executium/trending-historical-cryptocurrency-news (MIT License).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/nirholas/free-crypto-news
BugReports: https://github.com/nirholas/free-crypto-news/issues
